title: (x) Kansas State T-shirt - Europa {Mike Y}
content: It looks similar to [Europa Bold](http://web.archive.org/web/20050819172614/http:/www.fonts.com/findfonts/detail.asp?pid=205099). There seems to be a bit of flare at the ends of strokes, but maybe that is from the embroidering method?
author: bowfinpw
